<doc id="450025" wikidata="Q2646127" url="?curid=450025" title="Sichuan Daily">
<text>The Sichuan Daily () is a leading Chinese language daily newspaper based in Chengdu, Sichuan, China. In 2020, &quot;Sichuan Daily&quot; and the Sichuan Provincial Committee of the Chinese Communist Party jointly formed an international communication center.

